#
msgid ""
msgstr ""
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=utf-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:19
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_START\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As you land your ship, you realize that you are still able to see the "
"massive portal. Your concern grows deeper as you make out something massive "
"that landed a distance away. Whoever is there must have used a highly "
"advanced FTL jammer to stop you mid-jump, and they appear to be moving in on"
" your location quickly. If you have any last minute preparations, now is the"
" time to do them."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:22
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_START\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:29
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_GO_TO_FINALFIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Now fully geared up and ready for your final fight, it's time to see who "
"stopped you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:34
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The wait is eating you alive as the enemy ship approaches your location "
"until they finally slow down in front of you."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:37
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:39
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You can't believe your eyes when you see who stopped you. It's a giant flagship-like Obelisk vessel! Not any Obelisk either, they bear the colors of the Exterminators! Aenwithe is absolutely speechless, barely able to comprehend what he's seeing.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\"That design was never meant to be used ever again! Queen Y would never accept... Wait...\" Wither freezes as you pick up a hail from the other vessel. The pilot is none other than Queen Y herself, the leader of the Obelisks and the most powerful entity among all Exterminators.\n"
"\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"What? Surprised, Aenwithe? Frankly, you shouldn't be. Did you really think I would sit around and do nothing while you and your little friend go to wonderland together? Hah! Never! A queen of my stature would never let an enemy have the upper hand. Speaking of enemy...\" The queen turns to you with a glare, palpable malice exuding from her very presence."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:45
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Wait, the portal is still open!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:62
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Precisely, little fleshling creature. You led me right to their little hidey-hole, the last bastion of \"hope\" for a loathsome caste that should have been completely eliminated eons ago!\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tAenwithe blinks. \"Wait... that's why you brought the Exterminator... You... you want to purge them again!?\" Y laughs as loudly as her voice modules allow her to. \"Oh, but of course! We Royals are perfect in every way, and for these little creatures to continue existing... well, it would cast doubt on that notion, wouldn't it?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:67
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "If you want to hurt them, you will have to get through us first!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:69
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The queen laughs again. \"How cute. The measly mortal standing on the side "
"of failure thinks they can do it all. Well, it's your funeral, little one. "
"Not even that gruff admiral with their shiny white flagship could stop us. "
"What hope do you think you have?\" You see a huge fleet of Royal ships "
"jumping in. This might be the end..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:73
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Time to end this!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:77
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_jerry\"]/text"
msgstr "(Jerry) Hail Y."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:81
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_reborn_g\"]/text"
msgstr "(G) Hail Y."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:85
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_CASUAL\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr "(Vance Prime) Hail Y."

