#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:178
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_EXTREME\"]/choice/event/choice[@req=\"unique_vance\"]/text"
msgstr "(Vance Prime) Hail Y."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:186
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_DEATH_EXTERMINATOR\"]/lose/@text"
msgstr ""
"With your death, Y was able to destroy all remaining Commonwealths, this "
"time with no exceptions. After that, a short trip to your home reality was "
"made and with that, fell every single other faction..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:222
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_AUTO\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It appears this ship is also equipped with an advanced AI system. Now that "
"the crew is dead, it has taken control!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:228
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_VANCE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Y seems confused that Vance is alive and well, but confusion quickly becomes amusement. \"Hah! So you decided to deny yourself a worthy death? What a pathetic worm you are. What's your plan, little mortal? Run away like a coward again?\"\n"
"\n"
"\tVance doesn't respond. He simply stares Y down with an unflinchingly stoic expression."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:232
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_VANCE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:234
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_VANCE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Oddly, Y seems bothered by this, her temper clearly rising. \"What happened, little mortal? Too scared to even speak?!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tVance's expression changes slightly, a coy smile forming at the corner of his lips. \"No, this was simply a distraction.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tSuddenly, a huge explosion erupts inside the Exterminator's artillery system. \"You see, after so many years of piloting flagships, you learn a thing or two about their weak points. Just because yours is made of aether doesn't mean it changes the underlying physics.\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tBefore Y has a chance to reply, Vance shuts down the call, turning back with a wide smile on his face. It seems Vance managed to disable one of the Exterminator's artilleries!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:244
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_VANCE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:252
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_G\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Y becomes confused when she sees G. \"G...? What happened to you? And why are you onboard the mortal's vessel?\"\n"
"\n"
"\tG laughs, her unnatural red glow becoming stronger. \"Oh, my dear Y, you truly are clueless about anything outside your little palace, aren't you? Did none of your servents ever tell you about my disappearance? Or did you never care enough to notice that I was gone to begin with?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:256
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_G\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:258
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_G\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Y is taken aback from the sudden hostility. \"How dare you speak to your queen like this?! I demand you show some humility and KNEEL BEFORE YOUR GOD!\" Her temper flares and the exterminator shoots a warning shot towards your vessel.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tG isn't bothered by the show of force, however. \"Still as ill tempered as the day you ascended. No matter, your time has come, and I won't allow your temper tantrums to risk me dying a second time!\"\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\t\tSuddenly, the Exterminator's teleporting system starts glowing a deep red hue before catching on fire. Whatever G did must have permanently damaged it!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:266
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_G\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:274
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry stutters, unsure of how to react to the news. \"Uncle... He... "
"You...\" The queen laughs yet again, \"Oh, you are sad your uncle died a "
"failure? What a pathetic whelp you are. The multiverse will be a better "
"place without the likes of you around.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:276
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:278
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry collapses to his knees, shocked and speechless. \"You monster...\" "
"Jerry chokes up a sob, and holds his head in his hands while tears form "
"puddles on the ground."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:281
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr ""
"Jerry sits in the corner, crying. The Exterminator looms, its frightful "
"artilleries charging. You want to console him, but you have to get going."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:284
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:286
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly, Jerry gets back up to his feet, wiping away the tears. \"Well, "
"there's only one thing left to do now.\" He draws out a massive Gatling gun."
" You aren't sure where he got it from, but you don't have the time to "
"question it."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:288
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jerry"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:290
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:292
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With Jerry armed and ready, it looks like there's nothing left to do but "
"fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:295
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:301
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:303
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you begin your fight with the Exterminator, Jerry pauses, and walks "
"out of the room."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:306
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You have no idea where Jerry is going, but you follow him."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:309
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:311
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "Jerry enters the room where the Equinoid is sleeping..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:314
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You have no idea what Jerry is doing, and watch in confusion."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:317
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:319
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "Then, Jerry proceeds to mount the pony! \"Alright. Now I'm ready.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:320
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jerry"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:324
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"ponyc\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:334
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:336
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you begin your fight with the Exterminator, Jerry pauses, and walks "
"out of the room."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:339
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"pony_tamed\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You have no idea where Jerry is going, but you follow him."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:342
