"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:376
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "Jerry enters the room where Prince is sleeping..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:379
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "You have no idea what Jerry is doing, and watch in confusion."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:382
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:384
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Then, Jerry proceeds to mount Prince! The demonic Equinoid lets out a bone-"
"chilling neigh, ready to ride into battle. \"Alright. Now I'm ready.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:385
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "Jerry"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:389
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_BEGIN_THE_FIGHT_JERRY\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"fr_bonus_prince\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:413
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_POSITIVE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly, you receive a hail coming from the portal. \"Outsider! You showed us kindness in a way that no other being has ever shown, and for that, you have our support!\" You detect a few fleets jumping in, all aimed at the Exterminator!\t\n"
"\n"
"\t\"We've brought ASB fire and payloads to assist your fight! We'll keep the other Royal vessels busy. You just need to focus on taking down the Exterminator!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:425
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_POSITIVE\"]/triggeredEvent/triggeredEventBox/tooltip"
msgstr "The EMP Payload Surge will occur after this countdown."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:429
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_POSITIVE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:435
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_NEUTRAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Suddenly you receive a hail coming from the portal and detect a few fleets jumping in, all aimed at the Royal Fleet!\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\"Outsider! We'll keep the other Royal vessels busy as you fight the Exterminator. We're all counting on you! Regardless of whether we survive, it's been an honor to fight alongside you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:442
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_NEUTRAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:448
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_NEGATIVE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You shut your eyes and hope for a miracle, but nothing happens. You will "
"have to deal with both the flagship and the fleet all alone."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:453
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"FR_COMMONWEALTH_MORALITY_CHECK_NEGATIVE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:459
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You watch in triumphant jubilation as the Flagship explodes. You've won this"
" battle and saved the Commonwealth!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:464
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:471
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the flagship gradualy falls apart, you can't help but be proud of your "
"work here - You just saved a nearly extinct race from being completely wiped"
" out. Once you make sure the flagship is destroyed you perform a scan of the"
" area to see who's still alive."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:474
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:476
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You are soon hailed by what appears to be the commanding ship of the Commonwealth fleet. Their ship has taken a beating, but it's still standing strong. The other Commonwealth vessels have overwhelmed the royal fleet completely!\n"
"\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\"Outsider! You demonstrated high excellence and bravery in this fight, and your battle prowess was such that it could be written into song! Not only have you killed the being that kept us in fear at every waking moment, but you also destroyed their biggest weapon and symbol of oppression. For that, we are forever grateful.\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:480
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "We only did what we could. You deserve to live a happy and safe life."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:482
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Their makeshift leader smiles. \"Ever humble, I see! I'm sure that I speak for all the Commonwealth that from this day onwards, you are no longer an outsider, but an honorary member of our refuge! All hail our saviours!\" \n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tSuddenly your comms are filled with messages of dozens of obelisk ships cheering for you! Once they all calm down their leader speaks again.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\"Now, what's your next step, saviour?\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:488
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"We still need to defeat the Rebel Flagship back in the reality we came from."
" Do you think you could aid us?"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:490
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Gladly! Commonwealth! We march for one more battle today! Follow our "
"saviours and slay all those that oppose them!\""

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:492
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"-999\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:502
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:504
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The battlefield is pretty quiet after the fight. It takes quite a while to "
"get the attention of any surving Commonwealth ships. You find that only a "
"handful of fleet ships survived, all badly damaged, and some even unable to "
"warp away."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:506
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:508
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You ask if there's anything you can do to help, but the Commonwealth doesn't"
" seem interested in your offer. They worry that your presence might lure "
"more Obelisks to their refuge. They politely ask you to leave."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:510
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:512
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Not wanting to start another fight, you oblige. You chart your course for "
"the Federation Capital in hopes that there's still someone there left to "
"help."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:514
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:524
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:526
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The royal fleet is still standing, but they are too busy panicking after "
"seeing the Exterminator fall. Now is the perfect time to jump away!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:528
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:530
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With the Exterminator destroyed, any forces keeping your engine down are "
"lifted. You are able to swiftly escape back to the Federation Capital, "
"although not before an ASB shot hits your ship on the way out."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:532
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE\"]/choice[@req=\"fr_rep_commonwealth\""
" and @lvl=\"3\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:542
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_GOOD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You reach the Federation capital with a massive Commonwealth fleet by your side. In an instant, the Multiverse Flagship is obliterated by a giant fleet at your command with technology that is lightyears ahead of theirs.\n"
"\n"
"\tOnce the dust settles, Tully contacts you. After a few stressful moments where you try to explain what the hell just happened, he welcomes the Commonwealth to stay as long as they want. As a sign of thanks, he also offers to properly integrate them into the Federation!"

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:549
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_GOOD\"]/win/@text"
msgstr ""
"The future looks brighter than ever. Your tale will echo throughout the "
"multiverse for all eternity."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:553
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_NEUTRAL\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"It seems you've arrived at the last moment, as you witness many Federation "
"fleets being battered by an onslaught of Rebel ships. Fortunately, your "
"advanced weapons make quick work of the flagship, turning the tide in favor "
"of the Federation. In the aftermath, you contact Tully and tell him "
"everything that happened. What happens from now on is out of your hands, but"
" your job here is done."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:557
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_NEUTRAL\"]/win/@text"
msgstr ""
"This victory may not be what you were hoping for, but the work of a Renegade"
" is never over."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:561
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_BAD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You finally arrive at the Federation Capital, but it appears that you were "
"too late. The Rebel forces have already destroyed the Federation resistance "
"with the help of their Flagship and all Federation comms are dead silent. "
"You attempt to fight the Rebel Flagship, but without the Federation fleet "
"keeping the Rebel fleet busy, their ships are able to quickly swarm you. "
"Even with the aether tech you aquired, it isn't enough. As your ship falls, "
"so does this reality's last hope for the Federation..."

#: src-en/data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml:568
msgid ""
"data/events_fr_special_finalfight.xml$//event[@name=\"FR_FINALFIGHT_EPILOGUE_BAD\"]/win/@text"
msgstr "..."
